About This Music Sheet

A Wish (Final Fantasy XIII) is a song by Masashi Hamauzu. Use your computer keyboard to play A Wish (Final Fantasy XIII) music sheet on Virtual Piano. This is an Intermediate song and requires a lot of practice to play well. The recommended time to play this music sheet is 01:42, as verified by Virtual Piano legend, Arda. The song A Wish (Final Fantasy XIII) is classified in the genres: Final Fantasy, Songs From Games, Japan on Virtual Piano.
